rComments: I was approaching geography from a fine arts major, and this class / Wendy made everything make so much sense! Provided lots of time during the break and before / after class to address questions, facilitate discussion. Her slides summarize the important aspects of the textbook, you could probably do without it. Has lots of experience in the field!

Great professor & hands down my favourite class of the semester. Interesting material. My favourite part was her assignments - they were really practical and different than your usual assignments, e.g. attending a planning meeting, analysing a public space. They're a little broad but she gives you a lot of wiggle room to write about what you want.
